		<h2 id="chapter_project.inpage_nav_local_products" class="chapter__title chapter__title--destination illustration--local_products">Travel sustainably</h2>		<div class="practical-info">
			<div class="practical-info__header">
				<div class="image">
						<figure>
							<div class="image__body">
        <picture class="image__image">
<!--[if IE 9]><video style="display: none;"><![endif]-->
              <source media="(min-width: 420px)" srcset="/upload_mm/9/6/f/85170_fullimage_duurzaam%20shoppen%20per%20kilo%20werknemer%20met%20handenvol%20kleding%20%C2%A9%20%20abe%20jonker%20via%20kilokilovintage_560x400.jpg" data-focus-x="50.0" data-focus-y="50.0">
              <!--[if IE 9]></video><![endif]-->
							<img src="/upload_mm/d/b/8/85170_fullimage_duurzaam%20shoppen%20per%20kilo%20werknemer%20met%20handenvol%20kleding%20%C2%A9%20%20abe%20jonker%20via%20kilokilovintage_360x260.jpg" alt="Sustainable shopping per kilo employee with handful of clothes at Kilo Kilo Vintage" title="Sustainable shopping per kilo employee with handful of clothes at Kilo Kilo Vintage" loading="lazy" fetchpriority="AUTO" data-focus-x="50.0" data-focus-y="50.0">
        </picture>
            <div class="card__image-body-copyright">© Kilo Kilo Vintage</div>
							</div>
						</figure>
				</div>
				<div class="practical-info__text-container">
					<p class="practical-info__text">
									Did you know:
									<span class="practical-info__highlight">The sale of second-hand articles saves more than 150 tonnes of CO2 emissions per year.</span>
										<a href="/global/tourism/get-inspired/current/fashion/circular-fashion" title="Learn more about real impact" class="link link--arrow-right">Learn more about real impact</a>
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="practical-info__items">
				<div class="card-list">
					<div class="card-list__cards">
										<div class="card card--illustration illustration--countryside">
											<div class="card__text-body">
												<h3 class="card__title">
														<a href="/global/tourism/getting-around/interests/agritourism-activities-discover-the-dutch-countryside" class="card__link">
													Agritourism activities: discover the Dutch countryside
														</a>
												</h3>
													<p>Discover the Dutch countryside: where nature, adventure, and local flavours await you.</p>
											</div>
										</div>
										<div class="card card--illustration illustration--eating_drinking">
											<div class="card__text-body">
												<h3 class="card__title">
														<a href="/global/tourism/getting-around/interests/a-wonderful-wine-country" class="card__link">
													The Netherlands: a wonderful wine country
														</a>
												</h3>
													<p>Visit sustainable vineyards and sample the diverse wines of the Netherlands.</p>
											</div>
										</div>
										<div class="card card--illustration illustration--transportation_train">
											<div class="card__text-body">
												<h3 class="card__title">
														<a href="/global/tourism/getting-around/information/getting-around-in-the-netherlands/travel-by-train" class="card__link">
													The Netherlands by train
														</a>
												</h3>
													<p>The train is a great way to explore the Netherlands. You’ll be guaranteed to have the wind at your back!</p>
											</div>
										</div>
										<div class="card card--illustration illustration--leaf">
											<div class="card__text-body">
												<h3 class="card__title">
														<a href="/global/tourism/get-inspired/current/sustainable-holiday/the-netherlands-is-ev-friendly" class="card__link">
													The Netherlands is EV-friendly
														</a>
												</h3>
													<p>The Netherlands is extremely EV-friendly and makes it easy to explore the country by electric car.</p>
											</div>
										</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
